eiffel:
    play sound click
    if $data.crypto.metCrypto:
        choice:
            "There, outside that cafe... is that... it is! It's The Guy Who 100% Owns The Eiffel Table!"
            "[Buy a famous Pawrisian landmark. Fuck it, who even cares anymore?] <span class='prompt'>[[-1 ACTION]]</span>" if (>= $stats.actions.value 1):
                play sound spendAction
                set data.game_map.inMap false
                add_stat actions -1
                run transition_black cafe
                set data.global.cryptoEiffelDone true
                clear_dialog
            "<span class='prompt'>[[BACK]]</span>":
                jump game_map
    else:
        choice:
            "A guy appears to be making a big deal out of a table. Probably there's nothing better to do with your time than investigate."
            "[Buy a famous Pawrisian landmark.] <span class='prompt'>[[-1 ACTION]]</span>" if (>= $stats.actions.value 1):
                play sound spendAction
                set data.game_map.inMap false
                add_stat actions -1
                run transition_black cafe
                set data.global.cryptoEiffelDone true
                clear_dialog
            "<span class='prompt'>[[BACK]]</span>":
                jump game_map

    if $data.crypto.metCrypto:
        "The Guy Who 100% Owns The Eiffel Table is loitering outside a cafe, trying really hard to get literally anyone's attention."
        clear_dialog
        choice:
            talk nasty talk "Don't do it Ghost, you fucking mark."
            "I'll show *you* who's the mark, Nasty Girl! [Approach the guy who keeps making you a mark and get marked again]" if $data.ghost.investor:
                run skip
            "I'll show *you* who's the mark, Nasty Girl! [Approach the guy who keeps trying to make you a mark and get marked]" if (!= $data.ghost.investor true):
                run skip
        choice:
            "The Guy Who 100% Owns The Eiffel Table spots you approaching. He licks a slither of crab meat from his lips, and straightens his bowtie in preparation to receive you."
            "\\"Hello sir, it's me again. I don't care what your pitch is, I'm interested.\\"":
                play music bigmoney
                if $data.ghost.investor:
                    talk eiffel talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! I remember you, little lady! I trust your investments are serving you well? Certainly mine are serving *me* well! So well in fact that I thought I'd go for a celebratory walk, on which I have stumbled upon *this*!"
                else:
                    talk eiffel talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! I remember you, little lady! How lovely to see you again! My investments have been serving me so well that I thought I'd go for a celebratory walk, on which I have stumbled upon *this*!"
    else:
        choice:
            "The Guy Who 100% Owns The Eiffel Table is loitering outside a cafe, trying really hard to get literally anyone's attention."
            "[Approach the guy who is definitely not going to try and scam you] \\"Hello sir, I see you're trying really hard to get literally anyone's attention, and I just wanted to let you know I am completely down for whatever you have to say to me.\\"":
                play music bigmoney
                talk eiffel talk "That's mighty kind of you little lady! Why, you've really brightened my day!"
                clear_dialog
                choice:
                    "He grins. The sparkle on his teeth winks at you."
                    "[Blush]":
                        talk eiffel talk "I was just on a celebratory walk through town after making some big wins in the investment market, when I stumbled upon *this*!"
    clear_dialog
    "The Guy Who 100% Owns The Eiffel Table gestures to something outside the cafe with the energy of a pregnancy announcement. It is slightly wonky cast iron table."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk eiffel talk "What do you think? It's a real beauty, isn't it, little lady?"
        "[Look at the table] \\"Holy crackers! A table!\\" [Jump up and down in excitement] \\"Squeak squeak squeak!\\"":
            talk eiffel talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! Isn't it just dandy? Oh my oh my oh my, what an oh-mighty fine feat of engineering!"
            clear_dialog
            "He pats the table. It makes a horrible metallic sound and a bolt comes loose."
            clear_dialog
            talk eiffel talk "It's this kind of thing that just makes you want to give those muscular, sweat drenched boys at the factories up north a big kiss!"
            clear_dialog
            "He cups his hands around his mouth broadcasts his voice north."
            if (roll eiffel_north_orb orb 40):
                talk orb talk "That's west."
            else:
                wait 1000
            clear_dialog
            talk eiffel talk "Another job well done chaps!"
            if (roll eiffel_table_orb orb 60):
                talk orb talk "This table was made in Qing. Also, it's not a table, it's a stool. The factory fucked up and made it too big and now everyone just treats it like a table."
                talk nasty talk "Cunt-fucking-grats on the transition babe."
                talk lovely talk "Eugh! Vile language!"
                if (roll eiffel_table_nightmare nightmare 40):
                    talk nightmare talk "<span class='nightmare'>it knows what it is. you know what it is. we *all* know what it really is.</span>"
                else:
                    wait 1000
            else:
                wait 1000
        "[Look at the table] \\"It's okay I guess...\\"":
            talk eiffel talk "Oh yes oh yes oh yes! It's oh-kay oh-kay oh-kay! Not bad, but not quite good either!"
            clear_dialog
            "He turns you away from the table, as if not wanting to offend it, and whispers into your ear."
            clear_dialog
            talk eiffel talk "I'll tell you what though, it makes me think of something *far* more than just okay..."
    clear_dialog
    talk eiffel talk "You know what this beautiful piece of furniture reminds me of, little lady?"
    clear_dialog
    "He spreads his arms dramatically. Party streamers are flung from his sleeves and rain down around him, along with a single crab, which scuttles into a nearby sewer drain."
    clear_dialog
    talk eiffel talk "It's a dead ringer for the Eiffel Table, isn't it! The famous Pawrisian Eiffel Table! The Eiffel Table is *just* like this table is, but better! You know..."
    clear_dialog
    "He leans in to whisper at you, but doesn't actually whisper. He might actually be speaking louder than he was before."
    if (roll eiffel_loud_lovely lovely 40):
        talk lovely talk "He's trying really hard to make sure everyone nearby hears every word."
    else:
        wait 1000
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk eiffel talk "The Eiffel Table has been really taking off in the stock market lately. The Eiffel Table that is. I'm talking about the one in Pawris. The Eiffel Table."
        "\\"I notice you keep namedropping the Eiffel Table. Do you want me to buy it off of you? Because I'm totally open to that.\\"" if $data.ghost.investor:
            talk eiffel talk "Oh the Eiffel Table? Yes I *do* talk about it a lot. PERHAPS BECAUSE I *OWN* IT. And since you asked, YES IT'S FOR SALE."
            clear_dialog
            "He looks around to check everyone heard him. They didn't. There's a distracting she/her busker playing some really horrible (good) noise music on a black-market Soviet Theremin a few meters away."
            clear_dialog
            talk nasty talk "Classic. I once sold the Palace of the Soviets to a guy in Cawmden. Told him it was full of dicksucking fish, he seemed to like that."
            if (|| (== $data.crypto.boughtBridge true) (== $data.crypto.boughtSheep true)):
                clear_dialog
                choice:
                    talk orb talk "Okay. Fuck it. Buy the godsdamn Eiffel Table. I don't even care anymore."
                    "You think I should buy it? I wasn't that keen on it, but I you're right, it *does* sound like a good deal doesn't it?":
                        talk orb talk "Oh my gods. Ghost. How are you this dense."
                        if $data.global.couldntaffordhormones:
                            talk orb talk "You couldn't afford HRT, but you want to buy the most famous landmark in Frankreich, which a random guy in the street has told you he *totally* owns."
                        else:
                            talk orb talk "You want to buy the most famous landmark in Frankreich, which a random guy in the street has told you he *totally* owns."
                        talk orb talk "Okay. Sure. That's fine. That's the behaviour of a completely sound of mind woman."
                        clear_dialog
                        choice:
                            talk orb talk "Should we buy the big bong clock in Lunden next? The houses of parliament? Fancy saving up your pennies and buying the Fourteen fucking Cities?"
                            "Are those for sale too? I'm definitely interested...":
                                talk orb talk "Ḧ̸̫́Á̴̻̲͉̙̙̿̌͑̋<span class='nightmare'>A̷̧̩̗̰͕̒̌</span>A̶̝͍̥̖̹͕͐̇̄A̵̯͔̹̗͒͌̌̎̃̏<span class='prompt'>Ä̸̰͖́̊͆̌̉͠</span>Ą̴̹͙̑͂̏Ȩ̸͎̠̩̣̝̓͂̐́Ĕ̵̝̙͇̺͈̪͍<span class='magenta'>Ë̷̠́̒͠Ę̸̮͓͌̋̀̑͝Ȩ̴̥̫̊̋̈́̚ͅ</span>Ḛ̴̏͊Ë̴͇́͒̿͝Ẻ̵̬͉͍́<span class='gold'>E̵̦̭̿̍Ë̴̛̫̺̻͑̃̌͊</span><class='magenta'>Ẽ̷̦̥̂</span>Ȅ̴̼E̸̟̰͎̮̋͒̿͐̏̀͑<span class='prompt'>Ȗ̸̢͈̺͖̂̒Ư̵̡̘͓͓̜͆̌̅͝Ų̸̛̱̹̣̲̄́̈́̈͐͠Ṷ̵̦̭̺͕̜̇͛͘͝Ṳ̵͍̮̎̏̌͜U̴͓̤̇́͗Ŭ̷̬̑̉͂̈̎̚</span>Ũ̶̳̫͕̜̖Ư̵̡͈͖̔̑̋̚͠ Û̵̩<span class='nightmareQuote'>Ū̴̩͓̦̺͖͒̍̄̕ͅƯ̴̡̦̞̣̖̣̻̂̕͠</span>U̶̧̝͍͍̒̂̒͊͗̎̔Ű̸̢̻͇͑̔Ù̸͖̖̜͛̋͆̇̔͜Ū̷̻̫͙͖̫̓͛͂<span class='magenta'>Ú̶̫̮̾͋̓̃͝Ṳ̵̢̩̃̅̎́̐͝Á̵̫̻̖̊Á̷̜̥͇̺̖̗̓͘ͅ</span>A̷̓̈̌̌̋̈́̿͜Ű̸̢̻͇͑̔Ā̶̘͎<span class='gold'>Ạ̷̊Ǎ̴̹̩̠͙̳͕Ǎ̴̹̩̠͙̳͕Ǎ̴̹̩̠͙̳͕A̵̡͉̗̓̂͑̇̂͊̃</span>Ã̵͈̳̤ͅA̵̯̞̫̒A̶̹͇͔̰̱̝̐͊̈̍̇̊͝Ã̴̰͍͉̙̔̌̔<span class='magentaTiny'>Ắ̵͆͆͜</span><span class='prompt'>A̸̖̪̾͝A̴̝̲̭̎͑̓̒̄</span>R̸̨̪͗G̷̨̩̔͝H̵̪̣̝͕̉H̵̪̣̝̉H̵̪̣̝͕̬̉!̶̩̱̖͒̄̔̃̄̀͜͝ͅ"
                                clear_dialog
                                talk lovely talk "Oh me oh my. Ghost, darling, I think you've given Orb a brain haemorrhage."
                        jump eiffel_buy
        "\\"I notice you keep namedropping the Eiffel Table. Please continue to do so as I am excited to see where you go with this.\\"" if (!= $data.ghost.investor true):
            talk eiffel talk "Oh the Eiffel Table? Yes I *do* talk about it a lot. PERHAPS BECAUSE I *OWN* IT. And since you asked, YES IT'S FOR SALE."
            clear_dialog
            "He looks around to check everyone heard him. They didn't. There's a distracting she/her busker playing some really horrible (good) noise music on a black-market Soviet Theremin a few meters away."
            clear_dialog
            talk nasty talk "Classic. I once sold the Palace of the Soviets to a guy in Cawmden. Told him it was full of dicksucking fish, he seemed to like that."
            jump eiffel_buy
        "\\"You know, I'm starting to think you might be some kind of scam artist. Only a schmuck would fall for your schemes. A gaggle of idiots, all investors are morons.\\" [Look to the side as if there were someone there] \\"I'm one of the good ones.\\"" if $data.ghost.investor:
            add data.global.sideGlances 1
            if (>= $data.global.sideGlances 3):
                unlock_achievement scoops
                play sound scoopsshutter
                choice:
                    talk scoops flash "You *are* one of the good ones, Ghost. One of my favourites!"
                    "\\"Holy crackers! There *is* someone there!\\"":
                        talk scoops talk "I've always been there, Ghost!"
                        talk scoops talk "The names Scoops, Scoops McGee. Where there's a story there I'll be!"
                        clear_dialog
                        talk orb talk "CRYPTID CRYPTID CRYPTID THIS IS A CRYPTID."
                        clear_dialog
                        play sound scoopsshutter
                        "Scoops McGee takes another photo of you with his camera. You're a star, truly."
                        clear_dialog
                        choice:
                            talk scoops talk "Pleasure to meet you mam! But I better scram! Perhaps I'll see you again soon! Like the stars see the moon!"
                            "\\"I love you Scoops McGee!\\"":
                                set data.cryptids.loveScoops true
                                "Scoops McGee is gone."
                            "\\"Okay. Bye I guess.\\"":
                                "Scoops McGee is gone."
                complete_objective cryptids scoops
                complete_quest cryptids cryptidsSuccess
                clear_dialog
                choice:
                    talk eiffel talk "A- are you okay there little lady? You're talking to yourself even more than normal!"
                    "\\"D- did you not just see Scoops McGee?\\"":
                        choice:
                            talk eiffel talk "S- scoops McWho now?"
                            "\\"He's my friend. I love him. I'm going to marry Scoops McGee one day. We'll mint our wedding vows on the bloke chain, or whatever it's called.\\"" if $data.cryptids.loveScoops:
                                run skip
                            "[Wave your arms about] \\"Scoops McGee!\\"":
                                run skip
                talk eiffel talk "O- oh. Okay little lady!"
                clear_dialog
                choice:
                    talk eiffel talk "Anyhow, on the topic of investments. I believe you may simply have misunderstood! I'd never dream of running a scam on such a respectful, and might I say, *pretty* young thing like yourself!"
                    "[Blush and twirl a finger through your hair] \\"R- really? You think I'm pretty? Aw crackers, first Scoops, now you... the boys are really lining up for me today huh...\\"" if $data.cryptids.loveScoops:
                        run skip
                    "[Blush and twirl a finger through your hair] \\"R- really? You think I'm pretty? Aw crackers...\\" [Blush]" if (!= $data.cryptids.loveScoops true):
                        run skip
                clear_dialog
            else:
                play sound scoopscharge
                "The smell of cigar smoke. Hot in your mouth. Tastes of nice."
                clear_dialog
                talk eiffel talk "Oh no no no little lady! Perhaps you've simply misunderstood your investments! I'd go through the paperwork with you but I don't have it on me! But believe me, it's all genuine bonafede monetary magic! And besides..."
                clear_dialog
                "He smiles at you, a cheeky smile stretched across his face."
                clear_dialog
                choice:
                    talk eiffel talk "I'd never dream of running a scam on such a respectful, and might I say, pretty young thing like yourself!":
                    "[Blush and twirl a finger through your hair] \\"R- really? You think I'm pretty? Aw crackers...\\" [Blush]":
                        talk nasty talk "This is so fucking embarrassing."
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                talk eiffel talk "So, what do you say, fancy buying the Eiffel Table off of your old friend here?"
                "\\"Fuck it! Let's go! To the moon! Awooo!\\"":
                    jump eiffel_buy
        "\\"The Eiffel Table? My friend says it sucks. I think it like, killed one of her friends and crushed half of Pawris, or something? I'll be honest my memory isn't so good so I could be misremembering what she said and she's kind of pretty in a sort of scrungly way so I was mostly just nodding along and staring into her eyes.\\"" if $data.global.writerEiffel:
            choice:
                talk eiffel talk "I- I see! Well little lady, I can assure you the Eiffel Table is in tip top condition! I just had him renovated! So, are you interested?"
                "\\"Fuck it! Let's go! To the moon! Awooo!\\"":
                    jump eiffel_buy

eiffel_buy:
    clear_dialog
    set data.eiffel.agreedPrice $stats.money.value
    set data.eiffel.agreedPriceText (numbverter $data.eiffel.agreedPrice)
    choice:
        talk eiffel talk "What do you say? For the small price of... say, how much money do you happen to have on you right now?"
        "[Rifle through your pockets] \\"Uhhh... %{$data.eiffel.agreedPriceText} pounds. Why?\\"":
            "He counts on his fingers."
            clear_dialog
            talk eiffel talk "Well I'll be! What a coincidence!"
        "\\"You're just going to say the Eiffel Table costs however much money I happen to have one me right now, aren't you?\\"" if $data.ghost.investor:
            var coincidence true
            talk eiffel talk "Oh no no no! Certainly not mam! Certainly not! So anyway, out of interest, how much *do* you have on you?"
            if (roll eiffel_buy_lie_nasty nasty 40):
                var nastyGirlAdvice true
                talk nasty talk "Say something pitiful, like one pound."
            else:
                wait 1000
            clear_dialog
            "The Guy Who 100% Owns The Eiffel Table waggles his eyebrows."
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                talk eiffel talk "Le clock est ticking, madam mouse L! Only petite minutes left to take advantage of this trez bone offer! That's how they talk in Pawris, y'know?"
                "[Rifle through your pockets] \\"Uhhh... %{$stats.money.value} pounds. If you say that's how much the Eiffel Table costs I'll be really mad!\\"":
                    if $nastyGirlAdvice:
                        talk nasty talk "Sure, or just ignore me you godsdamn bitch."
                        clear_dialog
                    "He counts on his fingers"
                "[Shrug] \\"I don't know man... like, one pound?\\"" if (&& (>= $stats.money.value 1) $nastyGirlAdvice):
                    set data.eiffel.agreedPrice 1
                    set data.eiffel.agreedPriceText "one"
                    "The Guy Who 100% Owns The Eiffel Table looks deflated. He becomes a low resolution static mesh asset that should only ever be seen from over 10000 units away."
                    clear_dialog
                    talk eiffel talk "Oh. One Anglian pound. Just one of them. One single penny. Yes. Okay. I see..."
                    clear_dialog
                    "He sighs, and then, as though an electrical current has been shot up his spine, he once more becomes animated. Burning his energy like a supernova to continue his little song and dance."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk eiffel talk "I'll tell you what little lady! For the low low price of %{$data.eiffel.agreedPriceText} Anglian pounds you can be the new owner of a (nearly) priceless Pawrisian landmark, and more importantly, a once in a lifetime investment opportunity!"
        "\\"Wow! With a deal that good how could I say no!\\" [Hand over all of your money]" if (!= $coincidence true):
            jump eiffel_bought
        "\\"Hey! You did the thing you said you wouldn't do!\\"" if $coincidence:
            talk eiffel talk "Well I'll be! What a coincidence! That just happened to be the price I already had in mind! Reality really can be stranger than fiction, can't it, little lady?"
            clear_dialog
            "He taps his head, pondering the universe."
            choice:
                talk eiffel talk "So anyway! What do you say?"
                "\\"I say... I'll take it!\\" [Hand over one Anglian pound]" if (== $data.eiffel.agreedPrice 1):
                    jump eiffel_bought
                "\\"Well, with a deal that good how could I say no!\\" [Hand over all of your money]" if (!= $data.eiffel.agreedPrice 1):
                    jump eiffel_bought
                "\\"Actually, I think I'll pass.\\" [March away] <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
                    play sound spendAction
                    talk eiffel talk "O-"
        "\\"Actually, I think I'll pass.\\" [March away] <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>" if (!= $coincidence true):
            play sound spendAction
            talk eiffel talk "O-"
    if (roll eiffel_buy_pass_nightmare nightmare 60):
        talk nightmare talk "<span class='nightmare'>You'll never pass. Brick.</span>"
    else:
        wait 1000
    clear_dialog
    "It's too late. You march away with your powerful transexual gait. The weak male is left behind in your dust."
    set data.crypto.metCrypto true
    jump goToGameMap

eiffel_bought:
    clear_dialog
    unlock_achievement invest_eiffel
    set data.crypto.hasEiffelTable true
    set data.ghost.investor true
    if (== $data.eiffel.agreedPrice 1):
        add_stat money -1
        play sound coins
    else:
        set_stat money 0
        play sound coins
    if (quest_started? crypto):
        run skip
    else:
        start_quest crypto
    play sound till
    "The Guy Who 100% Owned The Eiffel Table somehow makes a perfect cash register sound with his mouth."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk eiffel talk "The sale that was heard around the world! You won't regret this little lady, oh yes oh yes oh yes!"
        "\\"Finally, my minute or so long dream to one day own a large swathe of Pawris has been fulfilled! Oh if only the jerries could see me now...\\"":
            talk eiffel talk "Oh ho ho ho! Why I'd say their jealousy..."
            clear_dialog
            "He raises and eyebrow and grins."
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                talk eiffel talk "Or rather, their 'jerriesiey', would be the only thing rising as fast as the value on your new investment!"
                "[Giggle] \\"So funny... so funny...\\"":
                    talk lovely talk "Titter titter! Quite! What a charmer!"
                    talk orb talk "<span class='writtenText'>'Jerriesiey'</span>? What the fuck does that even mean? Let me kill this fucker. I'm so mad. I'm so pissed off right now. Fuck."
                    clear_dialog
                    talk eiffel talk "Oh ho ho ho! Oh little lady, you flatter me oh so so so!"
                    clear_dialog
                    "A couple of police men turn a nearby corner and look vaguely in your direction. The Guy Who 100% Owned the Eiffel Table tugs his collar and gulps."
                    if (roll eiffel_bought_police_nasty nasty 40):
                        talk nasty talk "Nothing to worry about ladies. I know these types anywhere. Their shoes are too clean to be action rozzers. These fuckers are on 'face sitting license' patrol."
                        talk lovely talk "You need a license for that? Even if you're a pillow princess and oh so light? Oh me oh my... I uh, I need to go deal with something, I'll be right back everyone! Toodle ooh!"
                    else:
                        wait 1000
                    clear_dialog
                    talk eiffel talk "Goodness me! Look at the time! I best be off! Take care now, little lady!"
    clear_dialog
    play sound footsteps
    choice:
        "The Guy Who 100% owned The Eiffel Table bows, stumbles over the cobble pavement, and jogs away. He disappears down the street in a cloud of dust and nutritional powder."
        "\\"Eiffel Table!\\" <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
            play sound spendAction
            set data.crypto.metCrypto true
            jump goToGameMap